<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Stefan Geyer und Jakob Schenk</head><p>Der Rat bittet im Namen von Hermann Murr, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Herausgabe der zu Obernzenn aufgehaltenen, in Miltenberg gekauften fünf Ballen Leder.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_30" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l1">Stephan Geyer 
<del rend="strikethrough">n </del> Vnd Jacob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l3">Schencken</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l4"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Stephan vnd Jacob / vns hat fürgelegt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l5">herman Murre <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jr Jm funff pallen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l6">leders cʒu obernʒenne aufgehalten habt / daʒ man Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l7">cʒu miltenberg kaufft hab / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l8"><expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> daſſelb ſein leder <expan>vngehınd<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l9">vollgen laſſen wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_30" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Stephan Geyer und Jacob Schencken </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Stephan und Jacob, uns hat fürgelegt Herman
                        Murre, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz ir im funff pallen leders czu
                        Obernzenne aufgehalten habt, daz man im czu Miltenberg kaufft hab.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, dasselb sein leder
                                <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vollgen lassen wöllet, als etc.
                        das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
